    "A surrogate model that can capture the \"True\" relationship as closely as possible can accurately identify the most impactful molecular features, LLM's performance determines the interpretability and credibility of the generated explanations.",
    "Additionally, it should be emphasized that the quality of the generated explanations is also dependent on the quality of the literature dataset provided.",
